locality: Dzar; C. Nepal, Mustang, Muktinath/Western Region

Annapurna National Park, near Ice Lake above Manang Village. GLORIA site: NP-MNG-SMB (2). Collaborative collection done by Tribhuvan University (TUCH) and Missouri Botanical Garden (MO). Collectors included: Suresh K. Ghimire, Robbie Hart & Choki Gyeltshen.
